sql:
SELECT name 
FROM characters 
ORDER BY name;

SELECT DISTINCT c.name
FROM characters c
INNER JOIN activity_participants ap ON c.character_id = ap.character_id;

SELECT name
FROM enemies
WHERE enemy_id = 1;

external_knowledge:
- High-attack equipment is defined as equipment with an attack power greater than 50; 
- The 'melee' game mode is one of the several game modes available, and ranking is specific to each mode;
- Characters can have multiple friends and can be part of a guild with a specific role.

sql:
SELECT name
FROM characters
WHERE character_id IN (SELECT character_id FROM character_equipment);

external_knowledge:
- The default guild is assumed to be the one with guild_id = 0.; 
- Poaching activities refer to those with activity names containing the word 'poaching'.; 
- The average sell value is calculated based on the sell_value of equipment items.

sql:
SELECT character_id
FROM guild_members
WHERE role = 'leader';

SELECT name 
FROM characters 
ORDER BY name;
